snippet.title: 3EALITY Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: 3EALITY is a challenging indie platformer and endless runner set in a cyberpunk world in which you control protagonist Meta in 3 parallel universes simultaneously. Face the different obstacles and dangers in each of the realities and stay alive as long as you can. It’s basically multitasking in the multiverse!
